Company Overview of Allegory Law, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Allegory Law, Inc., doing business as Allegory Solutions, provides software solutions for litigation markets. Its solution interconnects litigation knowledge, including case administration, evidence, witnesses, and case documents. The company’s solution is accessed from various mobile devices, desktops, and tablets. Allegory Law, Inc. was founded in 2011 and is based in New York, New York. It has locations in Chicago; Dallas; Los Angeles; Miami; Palo Alto; San Francisco; Toronto; and Washington, D.C.


175 Varick Street4th FloorNew York, NY 10014United StatesFounded in 2011



Phone: 646-201-0036

www.allegoryinfo.com







