Overview



    Allegory interconnects all of the critical knowledge that litigation teams must have at their fingertips in order to win a case.  We are first to market in an industry that is quickly reaching a tipping point, as more and more law firms are actively searching for a solution like Allegory.  Our clients include litigation boutiques, BigLaw firms (including some of the most prestigious in the world), companies and government agencies.  






